    <!-- ================================================== --> 
    <section> 
     <div class="page-header" id="choose" style="padding-top:5px"> 
      <h1>Choose an Education<small> </small></h1> 
     </div> 
     <div class="row"> 
      <div class="span12"> 
       <img src="../img/C11_0061_700.jpg"> 
       <h3>Choosing a college can be complicated.</h3> 
       <blockquote>
        <p id="footnote7-ref">“The beautiful thing about learning is that no one can take it away from you.” <small><a href="#footnote7">[7] B.B. King</a></small></p>
       </blockquote> 
       <p>But it’s a whole lot easier if you remember what it’s all about — an education. And if you want an education that does all the things we’ve talked about, choose a liberal arts education. </p> 
       <p><strong>So, before you choose a college, choose an education</strong>.</p> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </section>
   </div>
